INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [l0].[LibroId], [l0].[CategoriaId], [l0].[Id], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[Nombre]

) AS [t] ON [l].[Id] = [t].[LibroId]

INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [l0].[LibroId], [l0].[CategoriaId], [l0].[Id], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[Nombre]
    FROM [LibrosCategorias] AS [l0]
    INNER JOIN [Categorias] AS [c] ON [l0].[CategoriaId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [l].[Id] = [t].[LibroId]
LEFT JOIN [LibroImagenes] AS [l1] ON [l].[Id] = [l1].[LibroId]
ORDER BY [l].[Id], [a].[Id], [t].[LibroId], [t].[CategoriaId], [t].[Id0]

    SELECT [l0].[LibroId], [l0].[CategoriaId], [l0].[Id], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[Nombre]
    FROM [LibrosCategorias] AS [l0]
    INNER JOIN [Categorias] AS [c] ON [l0].[CategoriaId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [l].[Id] = [t].[LibroId]
LEFT JOIN [LibroImagenes] AS [l1] ON [l].[Id] = [l1].[LibroId]
ORDER BY [l].[Id], [a].[Id], [t].[LibroId], [t].[CategoriaId], [t].[Id0]

    SELECT [l0].[LibroId], [l0].[CategoriaId], [l0].[Id], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[Nombre]
    FROM [LibrosCategorias] AS [l0]
    INNER JOIN [Categorias] AS [c] ON [l0].[CategoriaId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [l].[Id] = [t].[LibroId]
LEFT JOIN [LibroImagenes] AS [l1] ON [l].[Id] = [l1].[LibroId]
ORDER BY [l].[Id], [a].[Id], [t].[LibroId], [t].[CategoriaId], [t].[Id0]

Executing controller action with signature System.Threading.Tasks.Task`1[Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.ActionResult`1[System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable`1[hoshibunko.Models.DTOs.CategoriaDTO]]] GetAll() on controller hoshibunko.Controllers.CategoriaController (hoshibunko).
2025-03-03 19:31:47.727 -05:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[AutorId], [l].[Descripcion], [l].[Nombre], [a].[Id], [t].[LibroId], [t].[CategoriaId], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Nombre], [a].[Nombre], [l1].[Id], [l1].[LibroId], [l1].[UrlImagen]
FROM [Libros] AS [l]
INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [l0].[LibroId], [l0].[CategoriaId], [l0].[Id], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[Nombre]
    FROM [LibrosCategorias] AS [l0]
    INNER JOIN [Categorias] AS [c] ON [l0].[CategoriaId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [l].[Id] = [t].[LibroId]
